#. ~ Description for {'str': 'APEX Mk 0 suit'}
#: .\items\suit\suits.json
msgid ""
"Prototype APEX suit of armor, printed the showcase the potential of the APEX"
" Armor Division projects. Offers excellent protection in melee combat."
msgstr "APEX 裝甲原型套裝，用於展示 APEX 裝甲部門項目的潛力。在近戰格鬥中提供卓越的防護。"

#: .\items\suit\suits.json
msgid "APEX Mk I suit"
msgid_plural "APEX Mk I suits"
msgstr[0] "APEX Mk I 套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'APEX Mk I suit'}
#: .\items\suit\suits.json
msgid ""
"AI-controlled suit of armor, the first model to be derived tangentially "
"using Bitter Logic. It is easier to wear despite increased weight and "
"volume. Thanks to optimizations in structure and AI's management of the "
"suit, Mk I features improved protection against external threats."
msgstr ""
"AI 控制的裝甲套裝，是首個利用 Bitter Logic 間接衍生的型號。儘管重量和體積增加，但更易於穿戴。得益於結構優化和 AI 對套裝的管理，Mk"
" I 在抵禦外部威脅方面提供了改進的防護。"

